{| class="wikitable"  style="margin:auto; text-align:center;"
|+ Catalan and Spanish cognates with different meanings{{sfn|Moll|1958|p=47}}
! [[Latin]] !! colspan=2| Catalan !! colspan=2|[[Spanish language|Spanish]]
