|-
|''en Raül, a l'estació de [[Manresa]].''||<small>the Raül, at the station of (=in) Manresa. </small>||Raül, at the [[Manresa]] train station.
|-
|''El meu pare havia mort, inesperadament i encara jove,''||<small>The my father had died, unexpectedly and still young,</small>||My father had died, unexpectedly and still young,
|-
|''un parell d'anys abans, i d'aquells temps''||<small>a couple of years before, and of those times </small>||a couple of years before; and from that period
|-
|''conservo un record de punyent solitud.''||<small>I keep a memory of acute loneliness </small>||I keep memories of poignant loneliness.
|-
|''Les meves relacions amb la mare''||<small>The my relations with the mother</small>||My relationship with my mother 
|-
|''no havien pas millorat, tot el contrari,''||<small> not had at all improved, all the contrary, </small>||had not improved at all, on the contrary, 
|-
|''potser fins i tot empitjoraven''||<small>perhaps even they were worsening </small>||perhaps it was getting even worse 
|-
|''a mesura que em feia gran.''||<small>at step that (=in proportion as) myself I was making big (=I was growing up).</small>||as I kept growing up. 
|-
