* [http://www.gencat.net/presidencia/llengcat/ Secretaria de Política Lingüística de la Generalitat de Catalunya]

'''About the Catalan language'''
* [http://www2.iec.cat/institucio/seccions/Filologica/gramatica/default.asp Gramàtica de la Llengua Catalana] (Catalan grammar)
* [http://www.verbs.cat/ verbs.cat] (Catalan verb conjugations with online trainers)
* [http://www.gereon.greenheart.es/catala.php?lan=en Catalan and its dialects]

'''Monolingual dictionaries'''
* [http://dlc.iec.cat/ Diccionari de la Llengua Catalana], from the Institut d'Estudis Catalans
* [http://ec.grec.net/cgi-bin/AppDLC3.exe?APP=CERCADLC&GECART= Gran Diccionari de la Llengua Catalana], from Enciclopèdia Catalana
* [http://dcvb.iecat.net/ Diccionari Català-Valencià-Balear d'Alcover i Moll]
* [http://www.trobat.com/servicis/dvo.php Diccionari Valencià online]
* [http://www.dilc.org/ Diccionari Invers de la Llengua Catalana] (dictionary of Catalan words spelled backwards)

'''Bilingual and multilingual dictionaries'''
* [http://www.grec.cat/cgibin/mlt00.pgm Diccionari de la Llengua Catalana Multilingüe] from Enciclopèdia Catalana (Catalan ↔ English, French, German and Spanish)
* [http://www.catalandictionary.org/ DACCO] open source, collaborative dictionary (Catalan–English)
* [http://www.websters-online-dictionary.org/definition/Catalan-english/ Webster's Online Dictionary], [[The Rosetta Edition]] (Catalan–English)
* [http://www14.gencat.cat/llc/AppJava/index.jsp Optimot: Catalan language consults, dictionary and thesaurus of Generalitat of Catalonia]

'''Automated translation systems'''
* [http://traductor.gencat.net/text.do Traductor] automated, online translations of text and web pages (Catalan ↔ English, French and Spanish)
* [http://sishitra.iti.upv.es/ SisHiTra] automated, online translations of text and web pages (Catalan–Spanish)
* [http://apertium.org apertium.org] [[Apertium]] ([[free software]]) translates text, documents or web pages, online or offline, between Catalan and [[Aranese]], English, [[Esperanto]], French, [[Occitan language|Occitan]], Portuguese and Spanish
* [http://translate.google.com/translate_t?hl=&ie=UTF-8&text=frontera&sl=ca&tl=en#ca|en translate.google.com] online translations Catalan <> English & several languages

'''Phrasebooks'''
* [[voy:Catalan phrasebook|Catalan phrasebook]] on [[voy:Main Page|Wikivoyage]]
* [http://www.surfacelanguages.com/language/Catalan Basic Catalan phrases (with audio)]

'''Learning resources'''
* [http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/Appendix:Catalan_Swadesh_list Catalan Swadesh list of basic vocabulary words], from Wiktionary's [http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/Appendix:Swadesh_lists Swadesh-list appendix]
* [http://www.parlacatala.org/ Learn Catalan Online with volunteers]
* [http://www.intercat.gencat.net/eng/index.html Interc@t], set of electronic resources for learning the Catalan language and culture
* [http://web.archive.org/web/20091027154219/http://geocities.com/learn_catalan/ Learn Catalan!], an introduction for the Catalonia-bound traveler
* [http://catalunya-lliure.com/recursos.html On-line Catalan resources]
* [http://www.parla.cat/pres_catalaenlinia/AppPHP/login/index.php parla.cat]

'''Catalan-language online encyclopedia'''
